  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC450">
        <l>ceyyā yeṉṉu muṉṉilai viṉaiccoṟ</l>
	<l>ceyyeṉ kiḷavi yākiṭa ṉuṭaittē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>

  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/250/mode/1up">250</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/250/mode/1up">250</ref>.</p>
<p>iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, itu viṉaiyiyaluḷ oḻintuniṉṟa oḻipu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>urai : ceyyāy eṉa niṉṟa muṉṉilai viṉaiccol cey yeṉṉuñ collum āmiṭaṉ uṭaittu eṉṟavāṟu.</p>
<p>'innāḷ emmillattu uṇṇāy' eṉpatu ; atu ceyyāy eṉpatu, atucey iṉi eṉṟumām.	(54)</p>
 </body>
  </text>

